text.tspan: Happy Holidays!
Happy New Year!
Thank you for being part of my life! Things have changed so much
for me in the last few years and thanks to supportive friends and
family, a new career, and a recently purchased house in a wonderful
neighborhood, I can truthfully say I have found my place in the world.
Without people like you, I would not be anywhere near where I am now.
Enjoy happy holidays and a great new year with your family and friends.
~ Patrick Ratcliff
